{"tid":2221753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Fred Perry即時停賣經典黑金款Polo　只因右翼示威者穿上","createTime":"2020-09-28T14:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T00:17:40.000Z","uid":35519,"like":5,"dislike":241,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"d68cdeb6531c4e1cbcc64b5798a902c6f18b1dba","tid":2221753,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T14:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJVP37b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEJVP37b.jpg&h=e7d4cbe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.towleroad.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/mcinnes.jpg?fit=1200,787&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.towleroad.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fmcinnes.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%2C787%26ssl%3D1&h=313d50f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFred Perry將一款經典Polo全線下架，全因該款Polo Shirt被指與新法西斯組織扯上關係。<br />\n<br />\n這家英國服裝製造商表示，對右翼組織Proud Boys穿上其黑色和黃色Polo Shirt感到「非常失望」，並宣布它將不再在北美和加拿大銷售該產品。<br />\n<br />\n「我們表明，如果您看到Proud Boys成員，穿上我們月桂花環的衣服或任何與黑色/黃色相關的產品，它們與我們絕對無關。我們正在與律師合作，控告任何非法使用我們品牌的人」Fred Perry在官方網站聲明中如是道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/fredperry/status/1309438732165091328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffredperry%2Fstatus%2F1309438732165091328&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=fb69888f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffredperry%2Fstatus%2F1309438732165091328&h=4476e0a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/fredperry/status/1309438732165091328</a>"},{"pid":"1f00d4206b4d96bc09585530db62340518dd7a1d","tid":2221753,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T15:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c7de246ca148db4104bd2ddb871d3b644be4c6","tid":2221753,"uid":28397,"like":17